Package: vitos-vit-bhopal
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, vitos-base, vitos-tools, vitos-monitor, cron
Description: VIT Bhopal site overlay (lab scopes, hostname, retention)
 Site-customization layer for the VIT Bhopal cybersecurity lab pilot.
 Ships the 8 standard lab-exercise scope manifests for the semester
 (recon-101 through capstone-801), the FERPA + India DPDP retention
 cron, and the per-host naming template that derives a stable hostname
 from the workstation MAC. Pulled in by the unattended installer profile
 only — not part of the generic VITOS ISO.
